snippet: Eric Bledsoe scored 22 points and Devin Booker had nine of his 19 in the fourth quarter, helping the Phoenix Suns beat the Toronto Raptors 99-91 on Thursday night....
lead_paragraph: Eric Bledsoe scored 22 points and Devin Booker had nine of his 19 in the fourth quarter, helping the Phoenix Suns beat the Toronto Raptors 99-91 on Thursday night.

headline.main: Suns Shine in Second Half, Beat Raptors 99-91
headline.print_headline: Suns Shine in Second Half, Beat Raptors 99-91
